natl (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Enrich user request with LLM before generating command.
  * Second pass: run --help for parsed commands and re-prompt for final command.
  * Structured user request (rule-based fallback when LLM enrichment fails).
  * Debian: postinst adds shell widget (Ctrl+G) for sudo user; postrm removes it on uninstall.
  * Build: .deb and artifacts moved to dist/ inside project.

